data.description: Welcome Home! 3 bedrooms and 2.5 bathroom on 2 levels allows for ample space for the whole family. A Florida room just off the back of the home - perfect for a playroom or additional seating area. The primary suite is located on the main level just off of the kitchen, while the other 2 bedrooms are just up the stairs. Located just a short drive to local schools, US 1, Vilano Beach and more! All information pertaining to the property is deemed reliable, but not guaranteed. Information to be verified by the Buyer.
